title: Andy Warstar - 05/01/07 Nim FM 102.3 - Complete Show
description:
Here&#039;s Andy Warstar playing on Scan Dot ORg, German Martin&#039;s radio show in Nimbin,

Oz! This performance was just prior to the Nimbin Mardi Grass 2007, the nation&#039;s

largest pro-cannibas festival. With over 10,000 people in attendance every year,

Andy was stoked not only to do the radio show, but to play on both stages at the

festival. This radio show was done on the full moon, as well and garnered state 

side attention by www.upstartradio.com out of San Diego.
